<template>
  <svg
    ref="svg"
    width="800px"
    height="800px"
    viewBox="0 0 24 24"
    fill="none"
    xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
  >
    <path
      d="M4 17L12 17"
      stroke="#FFFFFF"
      stroke-width="2"
      stroke-linecap="round"
    />
    <path
      d="M4 12L16 12"
      stroke="#FFFFFF"
      stroke-width="2"
      stroke-linecap="round"
    />
    <path
      d="M4 7L20 7"
      stroke="#FFFFFF"
      stroke-width="2"
      stroke-linecap="round"
    />
  </svg>
</template>
<script>
import { ref, onMounted } from "vue";

const svg = ref(null);
onMounted(() => {
  let observer = new IntersectionObserver(this.colorChangeOnScroll, {
    threshold: [0.1, 0.5, 0.75],
  });
});
export default {
  name: "menu-svg",

  colorChangeOnScroll: function (entries, observer) {
    entries.forEach;
  },
};
</script>
<style>
svg {
  color: white;
  width: 100px;
  height: 100px;
}
</style>
